# SSD Agent Workspace
#
# Pipeline: briefing → domain-spec → contracts → tests → implementation → review
#
# ┌────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Directory       │ Purpose                                      │
# ├────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────┤
# │ briefing/       │ Raw input + normalized.json                  │
# │ domain-spec/    │ spec.md (→ Scope Freeze gate)                │
# │ contracts/      │ openapi.yaml + schemas (→ Contract Freeze)   │
# │ tests/          │ BDD scenarios + TDD suites                   │
# │ implementation/ │ Generated code (→ Implementation Freeze)     │
# │ review/         │ Audit checklist + HITL sign-offs             │
# └────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────────┘
#
# Stack: FastAPI + Celery | Next.js + React | LangChain + Claude | PostgreSQL + pgvector
#
# Rule: persist all artifacts in structured output (JSON/YAML/MD) before proceeding
# Gates: HITL approval required at Scope, Contract, and Implementation freezes
